{"tid":754653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兒子曾接種長生疫苗 趙連海無奈嘆：若追究再被「尋釁滋事」","createTime":"2018-07-24T14:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T08:23:45.000Z","uid":51271,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c1950412fef15b8f32e191b27666a6dcaeba9e93","tid":754653,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:36:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E9%95%B7%E7%94%9F%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E8%B6%99%E9%80%A3%E6%B5%B7%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E5%98%86-%E8%8B%A5%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB-%E5%B0%8B%E9%87%81%E6%BB%8B%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E8%25B6%2599%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A5%2588%25E5%2598%2586-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB-%25E5%25B0%258B%25E9%2587%2581%25E6%25BB%258B%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=6AKR81sUGUeq1ap08EE1ciwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=376b0be7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E8%25B6%2599%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A5%2588%25E5%2598%2586-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB-%25E5%25B0%258B%25E9%2587%2581%25E6%25BB%258B%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&h=e750772f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E6%9B%BE%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E9%95%B7%E7%94%9F%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E8%B6%99%E9%80%A3%E6%B5%B7%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%E5%98%86-%E8%8B%A5%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB-%E5%B0%8B%E9%87%81%E6%BB%8B%E4%BA%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>曾經帶頭為「三聚氰胺」毒奶粉受害人維權的患病兒童家長趙連海，指出兒子去年6月接種過長春長生生物公司的水痘疫苗。他在無奈感嘆：「憤怒？追究？都無效滴！&hellip;俺也明白，再追究啥還會再被『尋釁滋事』&hellip;。」</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n趙連海今晚晚上8時在Twitter發帖指出，妻子翻看兒子疫苗記錄，發現去年6月接種水痘疫苗是「長春長生生物公司」，「但又能咋樣？憤怒？追究？都無效滴！因為俺已被『交代』了😂。當然，俺也明白，再追究啥還會再被『尋釁滋事』進班房滴，而那些因此得利的官佬依然不會有絲毫懲處。活到快50，才明白咱不過是個屁。拍張照片謹發此推是為記.....」<br />\n<br />\n趙連海連日以來就事件評論，他幾日前指出，「毒疫苗事件再次爆發，又能咋樣？紅黃藍幼兒園那樣無恥卑劣罄竹難書的事情都能不了了之，毒疫苗還算什麼」<br />\n<br />\n他認為，這次「毒疫苗事件」再次引發熱議，是發自國人對自身安全的警醒以及人類起碼的良知，「一個已經黑暗的無非形容的國度，如果連一點點尋求公平正義的聲音再沒有，那這國的所有人都不值得憐憫！如果連吶喊的聲音都禁止存在，那這國已不配叫國！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2008年9月，大陸三鹿奶粉被揭發含有三聚氰胺，事件震驚全國。當年趙連海的三歲兒子被驗出有腎結石，他拒絕接受當局不合理賠償方案，並成立了「結石寶寶之家」協助全國家長維權。2010年11月，他被北京大興法院以「尋釁滋事罪」，重判囚兩年半。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf223c3ad5935e2817c170c7673943bac771c67","tid":754653,"uid":104443,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"連蘇聯都冇當今共匪咁奸"},{"pid":"9f61cbf073093d03af13b7662729b0701e076684","tid":754653,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869a96a2b5283fbf3356009ba6cabf4dcd8a8563","tid":754653,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T22:04:47.000Z","msg":"中國就是這樣的地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed42e1b9df665aeab551c918b4ec5cdf247762f6","tid":754653,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4ea442fdcff79c6fe9a99594f23ee08d852825","tid":754653,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:08:30.000Z","msg":"亮劍了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819a675517fcb6c577d5d43a2b000d9c9d57fb4f","tid":754653,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa91e8c34790af7da036a525cec50b991ba70ff","tid":754653,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:12:38.000Z","msg":"個b而家點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n身中幾範劇毒<br />\n我諗起令孤沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎要去少林寺搵易筋經先化解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c920ef876e3bf9ead3458026dbbc36fa32780b64","tid":754653,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:14:04.000Z","msg":"黑撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a732c87a6c598e382a9ec5203d3d97ed0ec4afa","tid":754653,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f224bfc461acf33dd1a6112a1b7ba51cc3755def","tid":754653,"uid":65263,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"0aa91e8c34790af7da036a525cec50b991ba70ff","tid":754653,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:12:38.000Z","msg":"個b而家點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n身中幾範劇毒<br />\n我諗起令孤沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎要去少林寺搵易筋經先化解到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:22:43.000Z","msg":"啲和尚假㗎"},{"pid":"3dd4ef5d65880702d56b2ba3028a99c426b6a71d","tid":754653,"uid":49359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T23:26:02.000Z","msg":"過兩關"},{"pid":"d6bb25f5d5fbc74185e2b84d52334905e4505375","tid":754653,"uid":